> [baduser](#comment_28_1KTDVd4rtqErz3FcxPx2nTmr4CSR9Q7hcr): You have many hardcoded links that point to http://127.0.0.1:43110. Not everyone hosts the node on the same machine, for example I have mine installed on a NAS so your images don't load for me. Best way to link to the same host is to use links in the format of //12MVkvYGcRW6u2NYbpfwVad1oQeyG4s9Er/merged-CDN/15fDN4wasXuyS8krtKvrxEVmWWLz6Qh518/data/users/18ASnnFHznjoSDUR9b8UdBrz2p3RjzoeuG/obscura1615552163679.jpg so no matter what the host is it should work.
